      <li><strong>Freelancer Tax Platform</strong>: Our team embarked on building a platform designed to simplify income and tax management for freelancers, prototyped it by the TaxVantage app concept. To enhance financial transparency, we incorporated Power BI, offering freelancers clear, data-driven insights into their earnings, tax responsibilities, and overall financial patterns.</li>
