      <li><strong>Drowsy Detection System</strong>: Created smart eyewear using Eye Aspect Ratio (EAR) and yawning patterns to detect drowsiness, triggering alarms and SOS alerts to prevent accidents.</li>
      <li><strong>Revive: A Sustainable Fashion App (Ideathon)</strong>: Revive is an eco-conscious app we developed to promote circular fashion by enabling users to donate, recycle, or upcycle their unwanted garments. By partnering with various brands, we aimed to reduce textile waste while offering users rewards and discounts for sustainable actions. Collected clothes are analyzed and given a new purpose through donation or restyling. As a team, we focused on creating a seamless, impactful experience that blends technology with environmental responsibility.</li>
